{"tid":2101890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［我係分化撚］唔該馮達浚團隊麻煩入一入來","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T02:28:56.000Z","uid":290879,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d08704b70f07800922ce3191c64b3b93043233f","tid":2101890,"uid":290879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoZYuVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoZYuVy.jpg&h=d47c96cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOqpqtW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOqpqtW.jpg&h=bfe0d251&s={SIZE}\" />我係某間黄店老闆<br />\n前幾日見到何桂藍出post話想搵地方貼poster<br />\n<br />\n小弟就申請左<br />\n今日收到份poster<br />\n居然係eprint印<br />\n<br />\n然後有連登仔<br />\n<br />\n移動芹菜<br />\n獨孤求立<br />\n<br />\n叫我開post屌埋<br />\n馮達浚用保諾時印刷<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌鳩你<br />\n我地幾撚窮都好<br />\n每次印文宣都一定要搵黄店印<br />\n首先唔係錢的問題<br />\n係態度呀<br />\n仲話黄色經濟圈<br />\n食撚屎啦<br />\n選舉經費到最後又係落番藍店到<br />\n我選你托閪呀<br />\n日撚日都講緊由生活細節做起<br />\n你就帶頭做衰<br />\n咩撚野叫抗爭融入生活呀<br />\n好明顯你團隊出鳩晒問題啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"61a9320f6b988c3bfc47de94e207bbf9e02560b6","tid":2101890,"uid":52802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"樓主有口齒<br />\np牌一日開一個post<br />\n第二日果然遵守諾言<br />\n輕輕幫推"},{"pid":"d2cf03911cc63d2d337eae89313242f597709255","tid":2101890,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"[轉載］<br />\ne-print 老細唔係藍<br />\n只係真香港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNgzUn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNgzUn9.png&h=a1d8716a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZN7uWu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZN7uWu.png&h=0e6300ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bbd38ef836e761384b5574755f635705b9d5cac","tid":2101890,"ui